My very imprecise impression, just skimming the conversations and not checking the details myself, is that Nalin diagnosed this in https://github.com/containers/podman/issues/18631#issuecomment-1558184454 , and that @flouthoc fixed the c/storage behavior in https://github.com/containers/storage/pull/1618 / https://github.com/containers/storage/pull/1637 .

Those c/storage changes are included in Podman since https://github.com/containers/podman/commit/e5399aaf3c10b03124e4b6855bb3dd5b9a1135cc .

@flouthoc PTAL and correct me if I’m wrong.
